node.text: SO grateful to @allureaestheticsllc for helping me achieve the 👄 results I want over the past few months! Getting work done seems to be such a taboo topic, and with the right professionals and plenty of research, it can be done correctly and shouldn't be shameful. I am beyond happy with my results, and I'm looking forward to continuing to work with them throughout 2021.
